{"tid":1816982,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"【武漢肺炎】洪永城高價購入N95口罩　湯洛雯：買唔到口罩唔出街","createTime":"2020-01-08T16:36:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-08T17:48:55.000Z","uid":85180,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b784e0e8419e87e59abb8c58e2ba47b8e8cc93cf","tid":1816982,"uid":85180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:36:40.000Z","msg":"【武漢肺炎】洪永城高價購入N95口罩 湯洛雯：買唔到口罩唔出街<br />\n撰文：陳芷穎<br />\n2020-01-08 22:45<br />\n最後更新日期：2020-01-08 22:45<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n最近武漢爆發不明肺炎個案，陸續有市民從武漢返港後疑染上不明肺炎，令全港市民的衛生意識急速提升。洪永城（Tony）與湯洛雯（靚湯）今日（8/1）出席無綫（TVB）劇集《丫鬟大聯盟》宣傳活動時表示有留意香港的情況，而同劇的謝東閔因病缺席，Tony說：「原本會一齊幫《丫鬟大聯盟》拍online video，但係佢病咗嚟唔到，佢原本今日都話想嚟，仲有少少未康復，我叫佢留喺屋企，千祈唔好出街，而家你好危險。傳染咗畀大家就真係唔好。」靚湯贊同：「唔舒服唔好夾硬嚟，因為太多人嘅地方都驚。」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3825613/org/f94a5e7e7d039b1959cdfbc06d47e922.JPG/79on-GC6pyxo09U08HIsz7yTWEeXmdDFWOBBO1jgQTs?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3825613%2Forg%2Ff94a5e7e7d039b1959cdfbc06d47e922.JPG%2F79on-GC6pyxo09U08HIsz7yTWEeXmdDFWOBBO1jgQTs%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=39f7528b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n洪永城有留意香港最近的情況，叫謝東閔留在家。（陳順禎攝）<br />\n<br />\n香港出現口罩搶購潮，有藥房更將口罩價格提升多倍，Tony亦有留意：「而家啲口罩愈嚟愈貴，全部炒高晒啲價錢，自己喺背囊有準備（口罩）。」靚湯說：「都會準備，多人嘅地方。我前幾日搭完飛機，唔使驚。（洪永城：『搭飛機啫，唔係去武漢就得。』）我唔係，我去泰國，我都要戴口罩，平時我唔鍾意戴口罩，我驚皮膚會焗到生粒粒。但係而家都要戴口罩，下次我宣傳都會戴口罩。（洪永城：『宣傳戴口罩點見到你靚樣？』）」Gag嚟㗎！」<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/3825622/org/169b37ba69450608dbf69d11a1fd6b09.JPG/V30hk1NBIaf0gyOGjwvDHJSNAkV6EwfR6HctDOh3LQw?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F3825622%2Forg%2F169b37ba69450608dbf69d11a1fd6b09.JPG%2FV30hk1NBIaf0gyOGjwvDHJSNAkV6EwfR6HctDOh3LQw%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=1e805ad8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n為保障健康，洪永城以高價購買N95口罩：「$100一個。最普通白色嗰個唔work，綠色嗰個先work，醫護人員戴嗰個。我係買硬紙皮、白色，黃色帶。」靚湯就獨有一套方法：「我都唔出街嘅，我好少出街，宅女嚟，所以呢段時間盡可能唔出街，繼續貫徹我嘅作風。如果買唔到口罩咪唔好出街，橫掂你（Tony）都有女朋友。」"},{"pid":"350c654b1cddbcef82117ac9e1694bca79f40665","tid":1816982,"uid":56716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:39:08.000Z","msg":"想同洪仔翻雲覆雨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7dc911a77778bddc445998f48f6ceb9aabd500d0","tid":1816982,"uid":56716,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T16:44:44.000Z","msg":"為保障健康，洪永城以高價購買N95口罩：「$100一個。最普通<span style=\"color: red;\">白色嗰個唔work</span>，綠色嗰個先work，醫護人員戴嗰個。我係買硬紙皮、<span style=\"color: red;\">白色</span>，黃色帶。」<br />\n<br />\n即是洪仔用100蚊買咗唔work嗰個？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"770abb23e9b89767d8c7146d5c9c1022a8c366ea","tid":1816982,"uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"想成為洪b的口罩保護他！"},{"pid":"7085d4bb718559f484c9a8f2f315d8704948938f","tid":1816982,"uid":183383,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:18:18.000Z","msg":"100蚊買口罩<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/treat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d8dc2cf40e7bd40c1a83d8ba0cd78b259c750c0a","tid":1816982,"uid":89336,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"770abb23e9b89767d8c7146d5c9c1022a8c366ea","tid":1816982,"uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"想成為洪b的口罩保護他！"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:22:45.000Z","msg":"比佢用完即棄<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b0680ea1685f304ba89dce48e515545fae609f3","tid":1816982,"uid":82917,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"d8dc2cf40e7bd40c1a83d8ba0cd78b259c750c0a","tid":1816982,"uid":89336,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"770abb23e9b89767d8c7146d5c9c1022a8c366ea","tid":1816982,"uid":82917,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-08T17:14:46.000Z","msg":"想成為洪b的口罩保護他！"},"citedBy":1,"reply